	<h1 class="title">「日本語」玩游戏，你听说过课金党吗？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/147/small/147.jpg?1418116339" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">陈思吟 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-02-27 08:00:04 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/22841/medium/22841.jpg?1456376203" alt="" />			
	</div>
